{"tid":504570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熊貓糞便製紙巾 60道工序$52一盒","createTime":"2017-12-20T07:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:42:29.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"98018f1454de4a4e1f9b81e2405f7f52f8dcd946","tid":504570,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>熊貓糞便製紙巾 60道工序$52一盒</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1970000/1974244/20JCA003__20171220_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1970000%2F1974244%2F20JCA003__20171220_L.jpg&h=a7efcc2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">熊貓糞便紙巾包裝上帶有「黑科技」字樣。(網上圖片)</span><br />\n<br />\n大熊貓被譽為「國寶」，沒想到糞便都是「寶」，還可以用來造紙。中國大熊貓保護研究中心與企業合作，推出熊貓紙巾，稱經過60道工序處理及高溫消毒，確保衞生，但售價不菲，每盒逾50元。<br />\n<br />\n研究中心與四川犍為鳳生紙業簽訂合作協議，將四川都江堰、臥龍、碧峰峽三個大熊貓基地的熊貓糞便和食物殘渣供應給該企業，用來生產廁紙、紙巾等生活用紙，暫不生產書寫用紙。<br />\n<br />\n研究中心表示，一隻成年大熊貓每天會產生超過10公斤的糞便，被稱為「青團」；由於投餵的竹子並不會被全部吃完，每天還會產生約50公斤的竹子殘渣。這些糞便和殘渣過去都被當做垃圾處理，會造成一定程度污染。<br />\n<br />\n鳳生紙業董事長楊朝林介紹，大熊貓主要吸收竹子中的多糖等營養成分，竹纖維都通過糞便排出來。而在竹子造紙的工藝中，有一道工序正是堆積材料、降解果糖、獲取竹纖維。「這一步熊貓在消化過程中就完成了。」<br />\n<br />\n經醫用高溫消毒<br />\n<br />\n熊貓紙巾在生產中共有60道工序，包括洗選、蒸煮等，最後經過醫用氧氣高溫消毒，出廠前也會進行細菌檢測，確保符合國家安全標準。由於生產成本較高，熊貓紙巾價格不菲，每盒售價為43元人民幣（約52港元）。事件引發網民熱議，有人指「太重口味」，亦有人認為，這與貓屎咖啡無分別。<br />\n<br />\n編輯︰陳文華<br />\n<br />\n美術︰陳超雄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1970000/1974244/028_01_a_20171220_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1970000%2F1974244%2F028_01_a_20171220_L.jpg&h=3e9a1bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974244/%E7%86%8A%E8%B2%93%E7%B3%9E%E4%BE%BF%E8%A3%BD%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE%2060%E9%81%93%E5%B7%A5%E5%BA%8F$52%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1974244%2F%25E7%2586%258A%25E8%25B2%2593%25E7%25B3%259E%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B7%25BE%252060%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BA%258F%2452%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8286d0e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974244/%E7%86%8A%E8%B2%93%E7%B3%9E%E4%BE%BF%E8%A3%BD%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE%2060%E9%81%93%E5%B7%A5%E5%BA%8F$52%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92</a>"},{"pid":"5e5eb179430318055a90baa98a3626cb9a87ff3d","tid":504570,"uid":156363,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"今次又真係幾有諗頭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c624b6fc0ea4fae5221ee56b9a37fcb74322bc","tid":504570,"uid":158998,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"但咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c6936ad29138586f20afeae9e6920850f5943a","tid":504570,"uid":3180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"用屎造既紙應該用黎抹返屎忽"},{"pid":"f8e35195e96d00b1f7ef2688ec4af09922565fd8","tid":504570,"uid":23829,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">一隻成年大熊貓每天會產生超過10公斤的糞便，被稱為「青團」</span><br />\n<br />\n米田共青團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a546f2c762b8fa1e11a3c15ec9d11161a26d2b0c","tid":504570,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"確保符合國家安全標準<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8654bd66e74cf49cd76bb90fd203a6adb06a9ae","tid":504570,"uid":33645,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"有得炒既話等睇新聞爆強灌食物比熊貓迫大便賣賺錢."},{"pid":"84ef055acd2bb731855c222f6b784af1f8237829","tid":504570,"uid":73443,"like":0,